.status
  - if plan.milestones.present?
    = image_tag 'target.png', size: '32x32'
    - if (milestone = plan.upcoming_milestone).present?
      Next milestone is
      %span.highlight= milestone.name
      on <strong>#{milestone.target.strftime('%D')}</strong>
    - else
      You don't have any target milestone.  Milestone is important to give you direction.
    .quote &#8220;There is no one giant step that does it, it's a lot of little steps.&#8221; - Peter Cohen
  - else
    = image_tag 'attention.png', size: '32x32'
    Tips: Setting a milestone is useful and important.
    .quote &#8220;A goal without a timeline is simply a dream.&#8221; - Robert Herjavec



